![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/0bfc5319-a43d-402d-bf96-48de82c9d98d/Ultimate-Invasion-Interior-Textless+%281%29.jpg)

In this episode, the Major Issues crew gives you the rundown on the new Ultimate Universe in "Ultimate Universe 101: Intro to 6160!" The hosts dive into the four-part event **Ultimate Invasion #1-4**, where the Maker (the evil Reed Richards from the original Ultimate Universe) escapes to Earth-6160 and sets about rewriting history. Then, they break down **Ultimate Universe #1**, a foundational issue that introduces new versions of classic characters—including a heroic Doctor Doom—as they begin to assemble a team to fight back against the Maker’s influence. Tune in for a deep dive into Marvel's bold new direction and get ready to jump into Earth-6160.  
  
